milestones.description: David Gower has scored 5 hundreds in ODIs, the most for ENG breaking Dennis Amiss's record
This is the highest match aggregate (593) involving teams England & New Zealand in ODIs
Lance Cairns and Jeff Crowe's 70-run partnership is NZ's highest for the 4th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 66 between Glenn Turner and Jeff Crowe
Ian Botham has broken the record for most sixes (23) in ODIs, going past Greenidge's 20
